[I] A KDE utility that allows you to manage disks

[T] KDE Partition Manager is a utility to help you manage the disks,
[T] partitions, and file systems on your computer. It allows you to easily
[T] create, copy, move, delete, back up, restore, and resize them without
[T] losing data.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/partitionmanager/

